Task 5: Use Transforms for Asset Discovery
Subtask 5.1: DNS Resolution Transforms
Right-click on the example-corp.com domain entity.

Navigate to Run Transform > DNS > To IP Address [DNS]

Maltego will attempt to resolve the domain to its IP address.

If successful, new IP address entities will be added to the graph with automatic links.

Repeat this process for other domain entities to discover their IP addresses.

Subtask 5.2: Reverse DNS Transforms
Right-click on an IP address entity (e.g., 203.0.113.10).

Select Run Transform > DNS > To Domain [DNS]

This will attempt to find domain names that resolve to this IP address.

New domain entities will be added if reverse DNS records exist.

Subtask 5.3: Email Domain Transforms
Right-click on an email address entity.

Select Run Transform > Email > To Domain

This will extract the domain portion of the email address and create a domain entity.

A link will be created showing the relationship between the email and domain.

